
Raspberry Pi Updates
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get upgrade

GUI Modules
*PyQt - $ sudo pip3 install PyQt5 

Face Recognition Modules
*Cognitive Face - $ sudo pip3 install cognitive_face
 

Speech Recognition Modules
*Speech Recognition - $ sudo pip3 install SpeechRecognition
*Google Api client - $ sudo pip3 install --upgrade google-api-python-client
*PyAudio - $ sudo apt-get install python3-pyaudio

Motor Modules
*i2c - $ sudo apt-get install python-smbus
       $ sudo apt-get install i2c-tools
*Adafruit PWM library - $ sudo pip3 install adafruit-pca9685
